Resource Generation Gets 30-Year Mine Right For South Africa's Boikarabelo

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-31T08:00:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/resource-generation-gets-30-year-mine-right-for-south-africa-s-boikarabelo.html
Resource Generation Ltd. (RES)  said it
has been notified that it’s been granted a 30-year mining right
by  South Africa ’s Department of Mineral Resources for its
Boikarabelo mine.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
